- CMD

```
echo 0x2800 0x28FF | opy 'B:{import unicodedata;};{[print(chr(i),hex(i),unicodedata.name(chr(i))) for i in range(F1,F2)]}' | awk '{print $1,$2,$5}' | ruby -anle 'p $F[0],$F[1],$F[2].split("-")[1]' | xargs -n3 | sort -nk3
```

tsvファイル出力

```
echo 0x2800 0x28FF | opy 'B:{import unicodedata;};{[print(chr(i),hex(i),unicodedata.name(chr(i))) for i in range(F1,F2)]}' | awk '{print $1,$2,$5}' | ruby -anle 'p $F[0],$F[1],$F[2].split("-")[1]' | xargs -n3 | sort -nk3 | sed 's; ;\t;g' >dot.tsv
```
